DataElement.preferredName: Prior Therapy Acute Lymphoblastic Leukemia Administered Yes No Indicator
DataElement.preferredDefinition: The yes/no indicator for information related to the prior treatment of Leukemia with an acute onset, characterized by the presence of lymphoblasts in the bone marrow and the peripheral blood.

DataElementConcept.preferredName: Prior Therapy Acute Lymphoblastic Leukemia Administered
DataElementConcept.preferredDefinition: Information related to the prior treatment of Leukemia with an acute onset, characterized by the presence of lymphoblasts in the bone marrow and the peripheral blood. It includes the acute B lymphoblastic leukemia and acute T lymphoblastic leukemia.
